===Adjective===
'''contradictory'''

# that [[contradict]]s something, such as an [[argument]]
# that is itself a [[contradiction]]
# that is [[diametrically]] [[opposed]] to something
# [[mutually]] [[exclusive]]
===Noun===
'''contradictory'''  (plural ''contradictories'')
#{{logic}} any of a [[pair]] of [[proposition]]s, that cannot both be [[true]] or both be [[false]]

